{
  "texts": [
    "These principles seem to be altered in the subjects with dysgraphia along with dyslexia.",
    "The app is developed for Samsung Galaxy Tab A and children can use S-Pen with a rubber tip write or draw on the screen of the tablet App.",
    "Two tasks are available in the app, where the first one is a copy game and the second is a tunnel game.",
    "In the copy game, the students are asked to copy a few symbols and words to the canvas provided in the app using the stylus.",
    "The copying game is targeted for testing the isochrony and homothety."
  ]
}